To run the viz.exe file from NIST computer without a XAMPP / Apache server running on your machine, open a new Chrome window from the command line. Make sure chrome is completely closed:

### PC ###
	1. cd to the following path: C:\Program Files (x86)\Google\Chrome\Application\' (or where chrome.exe is located)
 	2. Run chrome using this command "chrome.exe --allow-file-access-from-files"

### MAC ###
	To run on a mac, assuming you have chrome installed in your applications directory, type this into the terminal:
		open /Applications/Google\ Chrome.app --args -allow-file-access-from-files
